<div>
<p>黃巢圍<placeName>陳州</placeName>幾<measure quantity="300" unit="days">
<num value="300">三百</num>日</measure>
<pc>，</pc>趙犨兄弟與之大小數<num value="100">百</num>戰<pc>，</pc>雖兵食將盡<pc>，</pc>而眾心益固<pc>。</pc>李克用會許<pc>、</pc>汴<pc>、</pc>徐<pc>、</pc>兗之軍於<placeName>陳州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>時尚讓屯太康<pc>，</pc>夏<pc>，</pc>
<measure quantity="4" unit="months">
